\v 12 Joon cwáain¹ tya' 'in tsaru'¹u' Apolos do. 'Áa¹mo gamɨ́³ɨɨ tyaníi¹i wa'a itsajǿø¹i 'naa' coon'¹³ 'in tsaru'¹u' catyaai² pe jo mo gali'iin²¹²in nano. Joon joo²¹‑o mi jǿø²i. 
\s1 'Aa²¹²‑o jin'² Poo² 
