\v 19 'Aa²¹²moo' fuu²¹²uu jin'² 'in jai'² lɨ́ɨ²i Cristo 'in néei¹ la caain²¹ lɨ sii²¹ Asia. La joon jon jin'² Aquila coon'¹³ Priscila coon'¹³ jileei'²¹ 'in jai'² lɨ́ɨ²i Cristo 'in uncaan²¹in inʉʉ tya'a 'e un'goo²¹o Dios. Jin'²in la 'oo'²¹ ru'¹u' coon'¹³ Ña'ñʉ'¹ʉ'.  
